verbose_text: In addition, guanidinates with bivalent metal cations such as EuC (NH) 3, YbC (NH) 3 and SrC (NH) 3 have been introduced containing a doubly deprotonated C (NH) 3 2- unit, the nitrogen analogue of the carbonate anion.7, 8, 9 In these salt like solids, the anion adopts a trinacria motif, and then the amount of hydrogen bonding is insignificant.
